            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl3_Label1"><p>Iperius Console is a complete software for IT management and remote monitoring of workstations and servers. With Iperius Console it is possible to check the health status of remote computers and the status of the backup procedures, thanks to the integration with the other products of the Iperius suite. Starting from version 2.2.0, Iperius Console [&hellip;]</p>
