        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl4_Label1"><p>Iperius Console is a software for centralized management and monitoring of PCs, servers and backup procedures. Iperius Console can be tested and purchased from its official website: https://www.iperiusconsole.com. Following the purchase, we will receive access credentials and a license code. Starting from version 2.2.0, Iperius Console also allows Remote Desktop connections using Iperius Remote, therefore using the remote support [&hellip;]</p>
