        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl7_Label1"><p>In this article we will talk about how to install docker and what is container virtualization. Forget about the times when virtual machines were needed to test an application or to evaluate a particular infrastructure. Long start-up times, with considerable commitment to resources and physical memory space, and often scarce and questionable results. Today there [&hellip;]</p>
