            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><hr /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl8_Label1"><p>If you have a very old version of Iperius Backup installed, for example before 5, it can happen sometimes that the auto-update procedure does not work properly, returning the error &#8220;HTTP/1.1 301 Moved Permanently&#8221;. This error occurs when executing the auto-update procedure, clicking the button shown in the image below: The error is simply due to [&hellip;]</p>
